						               													<description>&amp;quot;The Ultimate Game of Chance&amp;quot;. A roll and move game for up to 6 players with elements of blackjack, roulette and mock-poker.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player starts with $3300. The game is played by rolling a die and moving around the linear board. Squares you land on may tell you to draw a 'Blind Bid' card, or if you land on a Casino space you will be instructed as to which of the three casino games you must play, and what the minimum bid is.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the rule book: &amp;quot;The object of the game is for all players to start at the airport and travel around the Financial Gaming Minefield, along the strip to Downtown and then back again as directed by the arrows on the board. Players to involve other players when playing Blackjack and Roulette. The player who reaches the airport at the finish with the most money is the winner.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
